# Library Layout

Project-specific firmware libraries live here. The active controller library is
`lib/Luefterklappe`.

## Luefterklappe

`lib/Luefterklappe/src` is the MCU-independent firmware core. Keep Arduino,
RP2040 and board-specific code out of this layer.

Main modules:

- `FanFlapController.*`: state machine, homing, safe position, soft endstops,
  fault handling and service text commands.
- `ModbusRtuServer.*`: Modbus RTU slave, CRC16, address filtering, register
  map and exception responses.
- `Tmc2209Driver.*`: TMC2209 UART datagrams, CRC, configuration and
  StallGuard polling.
- `PersistentSettings.*`: device ID and safe-position persistence with magic,
  version and CRC.
- `IoPorts.h`: HAL boundary for stepper, UART, delay and event logging.

Native tests in `test/test_controller` exercise this library without MCU
hardware through fake ports.
